": "近日，12 岁男孩深夜离家去坟地看妈妈的视频让众人落泪。 4 月 21 日凌晨，江苏南京一 12 岁男孩趁家人熟睡后偷偷离开家打车去老家。但因为忘记具体地址，出租车司机带着男孩向警察求助。 凌晨一点多，警察面前的男孩情绪低落，不愿意透露家庭信息和外出原因，执意要走。 在去派出所的途中，男孩终于开口—— 我就想去（妈妈）坟墓上看看… 作为父亲的警察瞬间破防，心疼地搂住了孩子。 这个孩子因为和父亲吵架，又在学校碰到了不开心，无法排解情绪于是想去坟地看妈妈。 孩子的人生路上，至亲至爱的离别最为伤人，很多时候却无能为力。 如何帮助他们排解自己的情绪，抚平曾经的创伤呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "78 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/460220425"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I6a/zyPq03PFEEAMaCDY0NTUxMDAzIKn2j4UGMAI4Q0Aecgk0NjAyMjA0MjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1621394060.7735896", "card_id": "Q_453352603", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 118}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "文人「肉麻」起来可以有多高级？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b014c7d17e9520bd53738aaa2ccc7b57_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/453352603"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I6a/zyPq03PFEEAMaCDYzMDI0NTc0IM2GtYMGMAA4rgNAH3IJNDUzMzUyNjAzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "32_1621394060.7739007", "card_id": "Q_459076670", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "三体人到底有没有折磨过云天明？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-feac21be82de778b39027f0a411ab659_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "66 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/459076670"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I6a/zyPq03PFEEAMaCDY0Mjk3NDM0IKjs7oQGMAE4lgFAIHIJNDU5MDc2NjcweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "33_1621394060.7742665", "card_id": "Q_454792574", "feed_specific": {"